plugins.description:
No more manual text layer updates. Just drop your i18n JSON file and update text layers automatically.How it worksName text layers with a dot-notation expression such as apps.welcome.titleStart the plugin and drop or select your JSON file.Text layers with names that match what’s in the JSON file will automatically be updated.The plugin only accepts the following JSON data structure:{
  "apps": {
    "welcome": {
      "title": "Happy new year 2021",
      "subtitle": "No more manual text layer updates. Sync your design with your i18n automatically.",
      "cta": {
        "hook": "Miso is good for you.",
        "button": "START"
      }
    }
  }
}

